            Steve Jobs was the founder and CEO of Apple Inc. - one of the biggest IT companies in the world.
          </p>
          <p>Steve Jobs is widely recognized as a pioneer of microcomputer revolution of the 1970s, along with Apple co-founder Steve Wozniak.</p>
          <a href="https://www.apple.com/in/stevejobs/" id="tribute-link" target="_blank">Remembring Steve</a>
