          <p class="quotes">“You can’t connect the dots looking forward; you can only connect them looking backward. So you have to trust that the dots will somehow connect in your future.”</p>
          <p class="quotes">“Your time is limited, so don’t waste it living someone else’s life.”</p>
          <p class="quotes">“Don’t let the noise of others’ opinions drown out your own inner voice.”</p>
